text:
Engaged Subraa to create my law firm website - Low Law Corporation - from scratch.

Mr. Subra was patient, knowledgeable and creative throughout the process. We worked closely in the design and intricacies of the website and I was well and truly satisfied with the results. So were my friends, clients and anyone else who saw the website.

A big thank you to Mr. Subra and the team. Here's wishing you all the best and to many more satisfied customers!

We hired Subraa for our company website design and development. A professional freelancer who helped us setup our company website within a short time. We have a long term relation of 5 years and Subraa helps us with the website maintenance, emails and our IT queries.

Subraa is always reachable though it is a public holiday or after office hours. Best web designer to hire, a great value for money.

This is the first time I engaged a website and logo designer, and Subraa has set a bar that left me absolutely satisfied. The quality of his work does not need further elaboration from me, but what I must commend here is his after-sale service and support. After delivery of the deliverables, he still made himself available for me to troubleshoot issues or to help me familiarise myself with Wordpress. Superbly attentive and helpful. He is my go-to guy for subsequent work.
I got Subraa to do a store name design for my minimart. He gave me more than expected variations, all of amazing quality. More than happy with his dedicated work. Keep it up Subraa!

Subraa's a very experienced and professional freelancer. He knows web development inside out. He delivers a consistently fantastic product, and was able to adapt to my requests seamlessly. Highly recommended for any type of web development.
